                           Hausfrau</roleName> Katrei</rs>.</rs></rs>
            </p></div><div type="seal"><p><rs type="event" ref="#ev__QGW_II_I_197">Besiegelt : <rs type="fn" role="witness"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__niklas_von_moedling_QGW_II_I_197">1. von dem
